Author: Aleph0-4
Text: ED thoughts and behaviours are on a spectrum of severity so there's no such thing as 'fake' or 'real'. just because other people might struggle more doesn't mean your problems arent' valid or that you're a 'failure' otherwise we'd all be failures because none of us have actually died from it

Author: senslessshit
Text: you can feel fake, but trust me, you're not. there is no such thing as being a fake ed sufferer. hope you'll feel a little better about yourself <3
